Introduction

Chung Ha is a South Korean singer-songwriter and dancer under MORE VISION. She is a former member of the Mnet project girl group I.O.I.

She made her solo debut on June 6th, 2017, with the mini album Hands on Me.

On October 10th, 2023, Chung Ha signed an exclusive contract with Jay Park's label MORE VISION.
